lines.text: Lots and lots of big trees together equals big trees!
Lots and lots of trees together... equal... big trees!
There was this one guy, and he was like, 'Suppa! Dat's suppa!'
No, no, this is "Secrets and Lies"...
[in girly English accent]
What do you reckon... you'll be doing... five years from now?

[about photo shoots]
It's weird because you always wanna do something original, and something new - but there are only so many poses you can do. And they want you to be natural.
Yeah, be normal, act natural... do this.
I am about to launch myself a hundred and fifty feet in the air! I feel queasy!

[to his little sister while holding a python]
No, it won't eat you. But when they get really big, they get HUGE! And then they strangle you - and then they eat you.
Look what you did to his shirt!
[Torn by fans at Paramus Mall]
It's like, an idecent killer fish!

[In a scottish accent]
They ripped my body out apart!
They killed mah family!

[about the Paramus Mall appearance]
We pulled up to the mall, and it was just packed, and we were like "Oh - Sears is having a sale." And then we were all "Well, maybe they're here to see us." - just totally joking, and then they opened the doors and this SHRILL scream just starts and we were like, "Oh..."
"We have a situation."

[after jumping into a pool]
Look what you did to his shirt!
[Torn by fans at Paramus Mall]
It's like, an idecent killer fish!

[In a scottish accent]
They ripped my body out apart!
They killed mah family!
